F_1 + F_2 +.....+ F_n = F_{n+2} -1 
S(k)
F_k = F_{k+2} -1 
S(k+1)
F_{k+1} =F_{((k+1)+2)} -1
F_{k+1} + F_{k+2}-1
F_n=F_{n-1}+F_{n-2}
F_{n+2}+F_{n+1}=?
F_{n+2}
=F_{n}+F_{n+1}
=F_{n}+(F_{n-1}+F_{n})
=F_{n}+F_{n-1}+(F_{n-2}+F_{n-1})
=F_{n}+F_{n-1}+F_{n-2}+(F_{n-3}+F_{n-2})
=F_{n}+F_{n-1}+\cdots+F_4+(F_3+F_4)
=F_{n}+F_{n-1}+\cdots+F_3+(F_2+F_3)
=F_{n}+F_{n-1}+\cdots+F_2+(F_1+F_2)
F_2 = 1
F_{n+2} - 1 = F_1+F_2+\cdots+F_n
